@startuml
title Kisan Sahayak - DFD Level 0 (Context Diagram)

' External Entities
actor "Farmer/User" as Farmer #gold
actor "Weather API" as Weather #lightblue
actor "Market Mandi" as Market #lightgreen
actor "Govt Schemes DB" as Govt #orange

' Central Process
circle "Kisan Sahayak\nSystem" as System #lightcyan

' Data Flows
Farmer --> System : Crop Details\nGrowth Stage\nLocation
System --> Farmer : Farming Advice\nCrop Progress\nAlerts
Weather --> System : Weather Data\nPest Warnings
Market --> System : Crop Prices\nMandi Rates
Govt --> System : Scheme List\nEligibility Criteria
System --> Farmer : Scheme Recommendations

note right of System
  DFD Level 0: High-level data flows\n
  • Farmer inputs crop/location data
  • System processes with external sources
  • Outputs personalized advice/alerts/schemes
end note

note bottom of Farmer
  Primary User:
  Mithapur, Bihar farmers
end note

@enduml

' Usage: Copy and paste at https://www.plantuml.com/plantuml/uml/
